## 1. Welcome

Welcome to {{ business_name }}'s AI Training & Awareness Guide. Artificial intelligence is transforming how we work, and as an organisation with {{ employee_count }} employees in the {{ industry | replace("_", " ") | title }} sector, we are committed to using AI responsibly, safely, and in compliance with Australian law.

This guide covers:
- What AI tools you can and cannot use
- How to handle data safely with AI
- Your legal obligations
- What to do if something goes wrong

**Completion of this training is mandatory and must be refreshed {{ training_frequency | replace("_", " ") }}.**

